examples.text: Dünyanın en çok petrol ihraç eden ülkesi, Suudi Arabistan'dır.
examples.translation: The country which exports the most oil in the world is Saudi Arabia.

etymology: Inherited from Ottoman Turkish اخراج ایتمك (ihrac etmek). By surface analysis, ihraç (“banishment, export”) + etmek (“to do”, makes verbs from nouns).
